"time":"2020-1-30 20:17","userId":"515251","userName":"丽奈的小号","userSign":"","message":"茜字怎么念，一般看含义。<br>读qiàn，要么是指一种多年生攀缘草本植物，茜草，要么是指红色。<br>读 xī，音译用字。多用于外国女子名。<br>茜新社，这个公司名字起的真是绝妙，你们懂的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">，官方念法对应罗马音是akaneshinsha，不是seishinsha，那么它的第一含义就应该是红色的新的东西<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">。但是我念xī已经念习惯了，大概也可以一语双关吧。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/44/17/441789.jpg","floor":"#15","id":"1555581","time":"2020-1-30 21:01","userId":"ubisoft","userName":"Ubisoft","userSign":"","message":"中文会在意，日文汉字不在意，反正在日文里也不读这个","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/43/20/432023.jpg","floor":"#16","id":"1555594","time":"2020-1-30 21:16","userId":"432023","userName":"七海千夜","userSign":"(小笠原学姐.jpg)","message":"还有名字里有柏字的","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/45/66/456600.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1555598","time":"2020-1-30 21:20","userId":"givemewings","userName":"べぇ","userSign":"(在買到ps5之前都不改簽名)","message":"朝陽的朝應該唸哪個","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/38/04/380419.jpg","floor":"#17-1","id":"1555599","time":"2020-1-30 21:20","userId":"poiuyyte","userName":"米人","userSign":"","message":"招吧"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#17-2","id":"1555618","time":"2020-1-30 21:42","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"","message":"我念chao"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/45/66/456600.jpg","floor":"#17-3","id":"1555621","time":"2020-1-30 21:49","userId":"givemewings","userName":"べぇ","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">鋭ちゃん</span> 说: 我念chao</q></div>只有朝陽我會唸zhāo，可人名碰過的是cháo<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/06/10608.jpg","floor":"#17-4","id":"1555626","time":"2020-1-30 22:06","userId":"vivid","userName":"庄生晓梦","userSign":"","message":"读cháo yáng时意思是向着太阳。读zhāo yáng时意思是初升的太阳。朝字的意思不同，读音就不同。"},{"avatar":"/